spec_data.Name: emacs-anthy-el
spec_data.License: LGPLv2+ and GPLv2 and Public Domain
spec_data.Description:
This package contains the elisp source files for Anthy under GNU Emacs. You
do not need to install this package to run Anthy. Install the emacs-anthy
package to use Anthy with GNU Emacs.
